original_title: Hitting The Highspots - Chris Hero 2016 Retrospective
overview: On this unique edition of Hitting The Highspots, Chris Hero sits down with Rob Naylor and covers his crazy year MATCH BY MATCH! Chris keeps a ledger with each match and gives a lot of insight into his crazy travel schedule, favorite opponents, different promotions, and all the good, bad, and in-between of being an independent wrestler. This shoot is a much watch!
title: Hitting The Highspots - Chris Hero 2016 Retrospective
